    "description": "Bata India Consulting Pvt Ltd invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Assistant Store Manager at our Gwalior location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Bata India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nBata India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bata India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
